questionsAndAnswers.question: How much time it will take to create the website / web application from scratch ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It depends upon the feature list, if you need the static website then it will take 2 to 3 weeks only.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide the website / web application with cross browser compatibility ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I’ll provide you a complete responsive website which will be compatible with all the devices and all the browsers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the duration of your support and maintenance period ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I'll stand as your backbone with your platform and will provide you 6 months support for any code related errors and will be available to you anytime when you get any issue or you want to extend further.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What would be covered in the maintenance period ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Free support included Fixing of any code related errors for 6 months but if you need any upgrades or you want to add any new features then that will be chargeable.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide the code of the website / web application or not ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you’ll get the complete code.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Who will be the owner of the website / web application ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You’ll be the owner of the website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How will I manage my website / web application ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will get an admin panel along with a guide document.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How frequently will I get the updates ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You’ll get a written update twice a weekly and detailed update at the end of every week.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you deploy the website / web application on my server or not ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I’ll deploy the final version on your server and will make it live.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you add content to my website / web application ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I’ll add content to your website but in ecommerce it will be limited to the number of products.
